Create a wordcloud component, called JSONWordCloud, listing the words that appear in a JSON feed.  Each element in the json array will contain phrases, or words; each separated by commas. there may be many rows. iterate over all of the rows, building a list of words or phases,  adding them to the wordcloud, with an increasing font size for the most used word or phrase. 
place the most used word or phrase in the centre of the cloud in bold